name: http_long
cmd:
keentune param tune --job http_long -i 20 --config 'ALGORITHM = tpe
BASELINE_BENCH_ROUND = 5
TUNING_BENCH_ROUND = 3
RECHECK_BENCH_ROUND = 4
[bench-group-1]
BENCH_SRC_IP = localhost
BENCH_SRC_PORT = 9874
BENCH_DEST_IP = localhost
BENCH_CONFIG = wrk_http_long.json
[target-group-1]
TARGET_IP = localhost
TARGET_PORT = 9873
PARAMETER = sysctl.json,nginx.json
'
